1
00:01:07,800 --> 00:01:10,080
All the sorrows between us.

2
00:01:23,280 --> 00:01:24,539
It's been so many days.

3
00:01:25,120 --> 00:01:28,720
Hasn't the news of your father's arrest reached the Capital yet?

4
00:01:29,720 --> 00:01:33,440
Or is this just a façade they created on purpose,

5
00:01:33,880 --> 00:01:35,479
to trick us into coming back,

6
00:01:35,800 --> 00:01:37,530
and catch us like rats in a trap?

7
00:01:50,800 --> 00:01:51,880
My Lord.

8
00:01:54,640 --> 00:01:57,039
I brewed this medicine especially for you.

9
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:05,760
It's way too bitter.

10
00:02:05,760 --> 00:02:07,420
Good medicine tastes bitter.

11
00:02:08,759 --> 00:02:09,090
Here.

12
00:02:10,479 --> 00:02:11,560
Eat.

13
00:02:11,760 --> 00:02:14,160
There's no one else here. Stop pretending.

14
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:14,920
My Lord,

15
00:02:16,520 --> 00:02:17,650
I've looked into it.

16
00:02:17,960 --> 00:02:19,280
Preceptor Qin suppressed the news.

17
00:02:19,280 --> 00:02:21,079
He said he trusts yours and the Master's character,

18
00:02:21,079 --> 00:02:24,079
and will discuss it after the witchcraft case is settled.

19
00:02:24,079 --> 00:02:25,200
In that case,

20
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:28,600
it seems the Preceptor values family ties.

21
00:02:31,040 --> 00:02:33,079
Fangji, you know him best.

22
00:02:33,760 --> 00:02:36,840
Could we have suspected the wrong person?

23
00:02:42,880 --> 00:02:45,940
The person who pushed my mother into the water back then

24
00:02:47,079 --> 00:02:48,520
was my teacher,

25
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:50,480
my uncle,

26
00:02:50,920 --> 00:02:54,160
the current Imperial Preceptor, Qin Heng.

27
00:02:57,280 --> 00:02:59,360
At first, because I lacked evidence,

28
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:02,080
I managed to stay by my uncle's side

29
00:03:02,440 --> 00:03:03,960
to gather proof

30
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:06,880
and find the truth.

31
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:14,400
It happened right when the witchcraft case was emerging.

32
00:03:15,040 --> 00:03:16,720
The two must be connected.

33
00:03:50,079 --> 00:03:52,600
He's just trying to fool everyone.

34
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:55,800
Fang.

35
00:03:56,480 --> 00:03:57,280
Fang.

36
00:03:58,360 --> 00:03:59,160
Fang.

37
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:01,800
Fang.

38
00:04:02,600 --> 00:04:03,800
You're finally back.

39
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:04,880
I thought you...

40
00:04:06,280 --> 00:04:08,740
I thought you died for the country on the way.

41
00:04:12,920 --> 00:04:13,920
You...

42
00:04:14,200 --> 00:04:15,000
What?

43
00:04:16,200 --> 00:04:17,600
Seen a ghost?

44
00:04:21,079 --> 00:04:21,959
Miss Su,

45
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:24,360
we are ghosts.

46
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:29,600
When someone dies with unrighted wrongs,

47
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:31,660
their resentment turns into a ghost.

48
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:37,040
But the Demon-Subduing Pestle is right here in Fang's hands.

49
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:40,840
Is this the surprise you told me about?

50
00:04:41,440 --> 00:04:43,200
It's more like a scare.

51
00:04:45,880 --> 00:04:48,960
Jian Boning and Lord Fang anticipated a mole.

52
00:04:49,280 --> 00:04:51,240
If we went to get the evidence rashly,

53
00:04:51,240 --> 00:04:52,640
we would have been discovered.

54
00:04:52,640 --> 00:04:55,680
So I discussed it with Jian Boning.

55
00:04:56,280 --> 00:04:58,280
We went to the wrong place

56
00:04:58,280 --> 00:04:59,680
to distract them.

57
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:02,120
Meanwhile, I sent the Heiyu brothers

58
00:05:02,120 --> 00:05:04,000
to retrieve the real evidence.

59
00:05:05,200 --> 00:05:08,480
Then how did you escape the poisonous fog?

60
00:05:09,880 --> 00:05:10,680
Don't forget,

61
00:05:11,120 --> 00:05:14,200
I've studied all kinds of Gu poisons and sleeping potions.

62
00:05:14,200 --> 00:05:17,160
Naturally, that poison couldn't hurt us.

63
00:05:17,240 --> 00:05:17,840
Also,

64
00:05:18,200 --> 00:05:21,600
we staged a fake death using medicine

65
00:05:22,080 --> 00:05:23,040
to fool them.

66
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:26,200
That is how we reached the Capital safely.

67
00:05:26,520 --> 00:05:27,320
That's great.

68
00:05:28,440 --> 00:05:29,280
Miss Su,

69
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:33,440
I'm sorry for making you worry.

70
00:05:34,280 --> 00:05:35,080
No.

71
00:05:35,960 --> 00:05:37,490
I'm just glad you're alive.

72
00:05:38,440 --> 00:05:39,770
As long as you're alive.

73
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:46,000
Heaven has eyes.

74
00:05:47,280 --> 00:05:51,560
My Su family can finally be exonerated this time.

75
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:56,000
Fang,

76
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:59,400
we have both the witness and material evidence now.

77
00:05:59,400 --> 00:06:02,460
Qingniang and I will disguise ourselves as your guards

78
00:06:02,480 --> 00:06:04,280
and go see the Emperor together.

79
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:12,160
But right now, the witness and material evidence have been taken by Qin Heng.

80
00:06:13,520 --> 00:06:15,520
Since we know where the evidence is,

81
00:06:15,640 --> 00:06:17,770
we just need to find a way to get it back.

82
00:06:18,200 --> 00:06:21,680
I'm an expert at picking locks.

83
00:06:25,360 --> 00:06:26,280
You're so annoying.

84
00:06:26,280 --> 00:06:27,540
Tricking me like that.

85
00:08:11,720 --> 00:08:12,640
Hand them over.

86
00:08:25,280 --> 00:08:26,140
Hand what over?

87
00:08:46,800 --> 00:08:48,320
Don't play dumb with me.

88
00:08:49,200 --> 00:08:51,000
You know what I'm talking about.

89
00:08:52,840 --> 00:08:54,600
Hand over the letters.

90
00:08:56,960 --> 00:08:59,120
Do you know what's in those letters?

91
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:02,400
Of course I do.

92
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:07,980
Then the recent witchcraft case,

93
00:09:10,160 --> 00:09:11,520
were you involved too?

94
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:15,280
Were you?

95
00:09:18,880 --> 00:09:19,920
Young Marquis.

96
00:09:21,600 --> 00:09:24,400
You know how many people died because of that case.

97
00:09:24,400 --> 00:09:27,530
You also know Fang Ji and the Prime Minister were framed.

98
00:09:33,280 --> 00:09:34,360
You know it.

99
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:38,280
The Imperial Preceptor is your father.

100
00:09:38,880 --> 00:09:40,800
You don't have to expose him.

101
00:09:42,360 --> 00:09:44,640
But you shouldn't aid his evil deeds.

102
00:09:48,760 --> 00:09:51,090
Aren't you just trying to help your father

103
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:52,680
by holding out?

104
00:09:54,920 --> 00:09:56,440
Why be so stubborn?

105
00:09:58,560 --> 00:10:01,020
As long as the real culprit isn't Su Ziliang,

106
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:03,160
does it matter who it is?

107
00:10:03,160 --> 00:10:03,960
It matters.

108
00:10:06,360 --> 00:10:10,720
My father was framed and killed for investigating the case.

109
00:10:12,600 --> 00:10:14,200
If he had just played it safe,

110
00:10:14,240 --> 00:10:16,640
he would have been promoted and rich by now.

111
00:10:22,320 --> 00:10:23,000
Su Zhaoxue.

112
00:10:24,040 --> 00:10:25,480
I'll say it one more time.

113
00:10:26,880 --> 00:10:28,800
Hand over the letters.

114
00:10:29,080 --> 00:10:30,080
Never.

115
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:35,400
Do you want to experience

116
00:10:35,600 --> 00:10:37,800
every torture of the Dragon Shadow Guard?

117
00:10:37,800 --> 00:10:39,080
I do want to try them.

118
00:10:39,400 --> 00:10:43,000
I want to taste every single torture of your Dragon Shadow Guard.

119
00:10:44,600 --> 00:10:46,480
I'm not joking with you.

120
00:10:48,280 --> 00:10:49,240
Yes.

121
00:10:50,640 --> 00:10:52,840
I know you're not joking.

122
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:57,000
If it were the old Young Marquis,

123
00:10:57,840 --> 00:10:59,840
he certainly wouldn't be like this.

124
00:11:01,440 --> 00:11:02,720
But you've changed.

125
00:11:05,440 --> 00:11:10,200
From a carefree, loyal, and sincere youth,

126
00:11:12,720 --> 00:11:15,120
you've become a pawn helping a tyrant.

127
00:11:15,120 --> 00:11:16,380
You don't understand.

128
00:11:20,040 --> 00:11:22,560
There are many things in this world

129
00:11:22,560 --> 00:11:24,160
that are beyond our control.

130
00:11:26,040 --> 00:11:27,680
I have my difficulties too.

131
00:11:33,920 --> 00:11:35,650
But it doesn't matter anymore.

132
00:11:37,720 --> 00:11:39,560
Anyway, in your heart now,

133
00:11:41,960 --> 00:11:43,820
I'm just a cold-hearted villain.

134
00:11:55,840 --> 00:11:56,700
Young Marquis.

135
00:12:00,360 --> 00:12:01,360
In my heart,

136
00:12:03,160 --> 00:12:05,680
you have never been a cold stranger.

137
00:12:08,640 --> 00:12:09,720
In my eyes,

138
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:15,320
you are the gentlest and kindest person.

139
00:12:17,360 --> 00:12:19,020
And the one who treats me best.

140
00:12:23,320 --> 00:12:27,840
Can you really watch the people suffer,

141
00:12:30,920 --> 00:12:33,000
watch the wronged remain uncleared,

142
00:12:35,920 --> 00:12:37,880
and watch yourself slowly

143
00:12:39,400 --> 00:12:41,120
betray your own nature?

144
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:50,360
Fine.

145
00:12:53,640 --> 00:12:56,840
If you don't want to hand over those letters,

146
00:13:02,040 --> 00:13:03,400
stay with me tonight.

147
00:13:31,640 --> 00:13:32,600
Rui.

148
00:13:34,200 --> 00:13:35,360
Why do you look

149
00:13:35,560 --> 00:13:38,280
so absent-minded today?

150
00:13:40,840 --> 00:13:43,640
It's just that His Majesty summoned Father today.

151
00:13:43,640 --> 00:13:46,400
It must be to discuss how to handle the witchcraft case.

152
00:13:46,400 --> 00:13:48,860
But Fang Ji and the others are still at large.

153
00:13:49,480 --> 00:13:51,280
I'm just a bit troubled.

154
00:13:53,280 --> 00:13:55,800
His Majesty is indeed furious about this.

155
00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:58,600
You don't need to worry about that.

156
00:13:58,760 --> 00:14:01,360
I will handle everything.

157
00:14:02,200 --> 00:14:04,520
Just guard the palace gates.

158
00:14:05,080 --> 00:14:09,040
Make sure Fang Yu's faction can't cause trouble.

159
00:14:26,760 --> 00:14:27,400
Father,

160
00:14:33,800 --> 00:14:35,200
must we do this?

161
00:14:35,800 --> 00:14:38,240
You and Uncle used to be so close.

162
00:14:38,720 --> 00:14:40,850
And His Majesty values you so much now.

163
00:14:42,360 --> 00:14:43,600
Ruilang,

164
00:14:44,360 --> 00:14:47,280
I have waited nineteen whole years.

165
00:14:47,960 --> 00:14:49,840
Nineteen years.

166
00:14:51,440 --> 00:14:56,640
Every night, I dream of your mother,

167
00:14:57,240 --> 00:14:59,760
covered in blood.

168
00:15:00,760 --> 00:15:04,840
Even if I'm burned to ashes for this,

169
00:15:06,240 --> 00:15:08,680
I will never stop.
